'''中国模式'''主要是指自1978年[[改革开放|改革开放]]后，[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]逐渐形成的一套[[中華人民共和國經濟|经济]]和[[中華人民共和國政治|政治]]的发展模式<ref>{{Cite web|title=聚焦中国模式|url=http://theory.people.com.cn/GB/40557/149513/index.html|publisher=[[人民网|人民网]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520193505/http://theory.people.com.cn/GB/40557/149513/index.html|archive-date=2020-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=中国模式挑战了西方典范，如今它走到了十字路口|url=https://www.nytimes.com/zh-hans/interactive/2018/11/25/world/asia/china-economy-strategy.html|newspaper=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|date=2018-11-25|issn=0362-4331|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210723030834/https://www.nytimes.com/zh-hans/interactive/2018/11/25/world/asia/china-economy-strategy.html|dead-url=no|archivedate=2021-07-23}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=什么是“中国模式”？|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/03/110302_cr_chinamodel|author=徐友渔|date=2011-03-02|authorlink=徐友漁|work=[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629093454/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/03/110302_cr_chinamodel|archive-date=2021-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=丁学良：中国模式核心理念不是个人自由|url=http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20181225-%E4%B8%81%E5%AD%A6%E8%89%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1|author=瑞迪|date=2018-12-18|work=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208231925/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20181225-%E4%B8%81%E5%AD%A6%E8%89%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1|archive-date=2019-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=德语媒体：中国崛起与中国模式|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%BE%B7%E8%AF%AD%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/a-50664326|date=2019-10-01|publisher=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003065757/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%BE%B7%E8%AF%AD%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/a-50664326|archive-date=2019-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What is the China Model? Understanding the Country's State-Led Economic Model|url=https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/frontline/article/china-trade-war-trump-tariff/|author=Abby Johnston|date=2019-05-17|coauthors=Catherine Trautwein|work=FRONTLINE|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913120827/https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/frontline/article/china-trade-war-trump-tariff/|archive-date=2020-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Is There Really a 'China Model'?|url=https://thediplomat.com/2018/07/is-there-really-a-china-model/|author=Bonnie Girard|date=2018-07-13|publisher=《[[外交学者杂志|外交学者]]》|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109014607/https://thediplomat.com/2018/07/is-there-really-a-china-model/|archive-date=2020-11-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中国模式最早是由海外民间创造的名詞，与“[[北京共識|北京共識]]”、“举国体制”等概念紧密相关<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":30" />。一般认为，中国模式以[[计划经济|计划经济]]、[[宏观调控|宏观调控]]等国家干预市场的手段来保证经济增长，而在政治领域依然保持[[中国共产党|中国共产党]][[一党专政|一党专政]]的[[威权|威权体制]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":30" />。中国模式出现了类似西方[[权贵资本主义|权贵资本主义]]的发展形式，故被西方一些媒体认为是一种政治上的[[獨裁政體|独裁政体]]与[[國家資本主義|国家资本主义]]的混合体<ref>{{Cite web|title=China's Crony Capitalism|url=https://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674737297|author=Minxin Pei|publisher=[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907193038/https://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674737297|archive-date=2020-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Crony Capitalism, the Party-State, and Political Boundaries of Corruption|url=https://eml.berkeley.edu/~groland/pubs/cronycorruptionv1.pdf|publisher=[[加州大学伯克利分校|加州大学伯克利分校]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613005324/https://eml.berkeley.edu/~groland/pubs/cronycorruptionv1.pdf|archive-date=2020-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=State Capitalism? No, The Private Sector Was And Is The Main Driver Of China’s Economic Growth|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/rainerzitelmann/2019/09/30/state-capitalism-no-the-private-sector-was-and-is-the-main-driver-of-chinas-economic-growth/|author=Rainer Zitelmann|date=2019-09-30|work=《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208202426/https://www.forbes.com/sites/rainerzitelmann/2019/09/30/state-capitalism-no-the-private-sector-was-and-is-the-main-driver-of-chinas-economic-growth/|archive-date=2020-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Why China clings to state capitalism|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/why-china-clings-to-state-capitalism/2019/01/09/5137c6d4-141e-11e9-b6ad-9cfd62dbb0a8_story.html|author=Robert J. Samuelson|date=2019-01-09|publisher=《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》（''The Washington Post''）|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210223511/https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/why-china-clings-to-state-capitalism/2019/01/09/5137c6d4-141e-11e9-b6ad-9cfd62dbb0a8_story.html|archive-date=2020-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[邓小平|邓小平]]等人曾在1980年代试图推进[[中华人民共和国历史#政治体制改革|政治体制改革]]，实行党政分开、权力下放、提倡[[法治|法治]]和监督等，但后期改革因[[六四事件|六四事件]]的爆发而失败<ref name=":18">{{cite web|title=80年代的政治改革为什么会失败？|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20141222/cc22wuwei42/|author=吴伟|date=2014-12-22|publisher=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021183337/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20141222/cc22wuwei42/|archive-date=2019-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":19">{{Cite web|title=邓小平的政治体制改革为什么没成功？|url=https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/12/%e9%82%93%e5%b0%8f%e5%b9%b3%e7%9a%84%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e6%94%b9%e9%9d%a9%e4%b8%ba%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e6%b2%a1%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%ef%bc%9f/|author=木然|date=2014-12-10|work=中国数字时代|publisher=《东方日报》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105120815/https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/12/%e9%82%93%e5%b0%8f%e5%b9%b3%e7%9a%84%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e4%bd%93%e5%88%b6%e6%94%b9%e9%9d%a9%e4%b8%ba%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e6%b2%a1%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%ef%bc%9f/|archive-date=2019-11-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":302">{{cite web|title=资料：赵紫阳在中共十三大上的报告|url=http://news.ifeng.com/mainland/special/zhonggong18da/content-4/detail_2012_11/04/18822143_0.shtml|date=2012-11-04|work=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]]|publisher=人民网|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021180914/http://news.ifeng.com/mainland/special/zhonggong18da/content-4/detail_2012_11/04/18822143_0.shtml|archive-date=2019-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

